1. *Govoriti* ću ti sve što znam. (I will tell you everything I know.)
2. Ona nije želela da *govori* o tome. (She didn't want to talk about it.)
3. Svi smo čuli šta je rekao, ali niko nije želeo da *govori*. (We all heard what he said, but nobody wanted to speak.)
4. On se nije osećao prijatno kada se *govorilo* o njegovoj prošlosti. (He didn't feel comfortable when they talked about his past.)
5. *Govoriti* se o toj temi je bilo tabu. (Talking about this topic was taboo.)
6. Znam da ti je teško *govoriti* o tome. (I know it's hard for you to talk about it.)